==Romanian==
===Etymology===
Perhaps from Latin ''*alninus''< ''[[alnus]]''. This Latin etymology is challenged by at least one current linguist, Sorin Paliga, who favors a substrate origin.
===Noun===
'''arin''' {{m}}, pl. ''[[arini]]''
#species of the genus ''[[Alnus]]''.
